features: 【Easily Adjustable and Expandable】This shoe organizer is designed to fit any space, with a maximum size of 34*14*10 inches. Never worry about sizing again!

【Space Saving】Boasting incredible capacity, this shoe rack features an elevated bottom tier that makes room for even more shoes! When fully expanded, it can accommodate up to 24 pairs of shoes, keeping all of your footwear neatly organized.

【Sturdy and Durable】Our heavy-duty shoe rack is made with thick metal tubes and natural rubberwood, ensuring a sturdy, free-standing structure that can hold up to 20 pounds per tier. No more worries about heavy boots, leather shoes, or basketball shoes cluttering your floor.

【Multifunctional Shoe Rack】Versatile as can be, this shoe rack is an excellent space-saving addition to any home, dorm, or apartment. Perfect for entryways, bedrooms, hallways, bathrooms, and garages, it's a must-have for anyone looking to keep their living spaces tidy and clutter-free!

【Easy to Install】With a simple and sturdy design, this shoe rack is incredibly easy to install without any tools required. In just five minutes, you can have it up and ready to go. Plus, the handle design makes it effortless to move the rack wherever you need it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Functional but Delicate
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This little shoe rack is easy to assemble and extends quickly, but I have to be careful when reducing the size. This is not really a problem for me as I always leave it fully extended. I just noticed while making the video for this review that it seemed like I could have broke it if not being careful. So, yes, it is a good shoe rack but is better off leaving either fully extended or not. I wouldn’t go back and forth with this. With that being said, it is strong when it comes to holding the shoes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent shoe rack
reviews.reviewText: It’s sturdy, fairly easy to assemble and a blank canvas. The wood parts can be painted or stained to your liking. I left mine how they are for now. The only thing I didn’t like is that one of the silver bars where you screw into, the white piece was pushed so far down into the bar that I couldn’t get the screw to screw into it. I had to get a small tool to pull it up higher so that I could screw in the last screw. If I wasn’t able to fix it, one of the bars would’ve been loose and wobbly. I’m glad it worked out. It’s a nice size shoe rack that’s sturdy and adjustable.
